{
  "name": "Filter",
  "summary": "<p><strong>Filter</strong> 对象是 <a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Filters/Filters .htm#Filters.Filters\"><strong>Filters</strong></a> 集合的成员。<strong>Filters</strong> 集合包含自动筛选区域中的所有筛选。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Filters/Filters .htm#Filters.Filters\">Filters</a></strong>( <em>index</em>)（其中 <em>index</em> 是筛选的标题或索引号）可返回单个 <strong>Filter</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将一个变量设置为第一张工作表上的筛选区域中第一列的筛选的 On 属性的值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilterMode</span>) {\n        filterIsOn = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">On</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例对第二列应用自动筛选器，并显示第一张工作表上筛选区域中第二列的第一个筛选值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AutoFilter</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Crucial&quot;</span>, xlOr, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Important&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Criteria1</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表单个列的筛选。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a>**对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>)\n{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回集合中对象的数目。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上筛选区域中第一列的筛选数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Criteria1",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回筛选区域内指定列上的第一个筛选值。<strong>Variant</strong> 类型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将变量设置为第一张工作表上的筛选区域中第一列的筛选的 Criteria1 属性值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilterMode</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> filter = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">On</span>) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> c1 = filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Criteria1</span>\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上筛选区域中第一列的筛选的 Criteria1 属性值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Criteria1</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Criteria2",
      "summary": "<p>使用筛选的 <strong>Criteria2</strong> 属性时，如果该筛选没有使用两个条件，则将出现错误。在试图使用 <strong>Criteria2</strong> 属性之前，需保证 <strong>Filter</strong> 对象的 <strong>Operator</strong> 属性不为零 (0)。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回已筛选区域中指定列的第二个筛选值。<strong>Variant</strong> 类型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将一个变量设置为 Criteria2 属性值。该属性是第一张工作表上已筛选区域中的第一列筛选的。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> c2 = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilterMode</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> filter = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">On</span> &amp;&amp; filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span>) {\n            c2 = filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Criteria2</span>\n        } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n            c2 = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Not set&quot;</span>\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上筛选区域中第一列的第二个筛选值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Criteria2</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "On",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果打开指定的筛选，则该属性值为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将变量设置为第一张工作表上的筛选区域中第一列的筛选的 Criteria1 属性值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilterMode</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> filter = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">On</span>) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> c1 = filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Criteria1</span>\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上筛选区域中第一列的筛选的 On 属性值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">On</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Operator",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 **<a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlAutoFilterOperator 枚举.html\">XlAutoFilterOperator</a>**值，它代表与指定筛选所应用的两个条件相关的操作符。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上筛选区域中第一列的筛选的 Operator 属性值是否为 xlOr。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> == xlOr)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上筛选区域中第一列的筛选的 Operator 属性值设置为 xlFilterValues。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> = xlFilterValues\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlAutoFilterOperator",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": []
}